          <li><a href={url("/repeaters")}>Quantum repeaters</a> — multi-hop entanglement delivery; relevant if inter-cryostat distances grow past direct-fibre reach.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/cisco-qunnect-brooklyn")}>Cisco × Qunnect Brooklyn–Manhattan</a> — Cisco's existing deployed-fibre entanglement-swap demonstration; useful contrast to the IBM superconducting-qubit roadmap.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/applications")}>Applications</a> — distributed quantum computing as the target use case.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/companies")}>Companies</a> — IBM and Cisco profiles.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

